The paper deals with a dataset and models for machine reading comprehension of Chinese judicial documents, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
